# Asset Placeholders for DevotionFlow

Required assets:
- icon.png (1024x1024) - App icon
- splash.png (1284x2778) - Splash screen
- adaptive-icon.png (1024x1024) - Android adaptive icon
- notification-icon.png (96x96) - Notification icon

Generate these with your preferred design tool or AI image generator.
Recommended: Use warm cream/brown tones (#F5F0E8, #8B7355) to match theme.
